text-node.description: This pipeline initiates one step check out for authenticated customer by populating default shipping, billing, and payment details of customer before dispalying summary page.
Sets Shipping address to basket based on default shipping address id.

decision-node.description: Check if first name and last name are present

text-node.description: Gets the default payment instrument applicable to the basket. If it is type credit card, we show it. If it is of type paypal, or paylater, we show the first non-empty credit card as selected

decision-node.description: Pick the first valid credit card
Check if the continuity payment method is not paylater. If this condition is false, we select the first valid card to show, and bypass this payment method

pipelet-node.description: Assign the first not-null credit card, as selected, in case default payment method was paypal or paylater

Sets shipping method to basket, if not available in basket.
Call checks for available biling address for user if not already present in basket.
Checks for available payment methods and sets to basket if not already avaialbe in basket.
Checks for available shipping method for user and sets to basket.
